entry.title: U.N. Inspectors Leave Kyiv for Zaporizhzhia Nuclear Plant
entry.content: An International Atomic Energy Agency team headed to the Russian-occupied nuclear-power plant early Wednesday, pledging to establish a permanent mission there amid fears that fighting in the area could lead to a nuclear disaster.
